    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "To add to this thread exploring ERC1155-tokenized roles, this a governance contract I have put into prod that allows mint/burn of function access (the ID is `uint32(msg.sig)` for brevity), https://github.com/kalidao/keep/blob/main/src/Keep.sol\r\n\r\nWelcome comment and testing of idea in form of ACv2, but I think the key benefit of ERC1155 for this use case is giving a single address to coordinate the roles and IDs as a collection of NFTs that are easily discoverable and can be balance-ranked for additional contract access rights.",
